Delicious pizza! We have ordered 3x in the past 2 weeks since we first tried this on May 31st, 2018. The first time my boyfriend ate the whole medium cheese pizza in one sitting. And had me order it again 2 days later cuz it was so good. We ordered 2 nights ago a 3rd time and I decided to try it with no cheese as I am vegan. I added broccoli, mushroom, onions, and black olives and it still only came out to $14. I added a fee chopped tomatoes at home. A medium cheese pizza is $11. Let me tell you that I finished that whole medium vegetable pizza in one sitting cuz it was so good! And my boyfriend finished his last night.  I couldn’t eat for a day or 2 after but it was so worth it! This is deff our go to pizza spot. The crust is great and they don’t skimp on toppings. Considering I even ate mine without cheese I can only imagine how much non vegans would enjoy this like my boyfriend! They are polite on the phone and delivery is VERY fast! They take 15-30 minutes maybe MOST. I am glad they’re in the neighborhood. Our #1 pizza spot here in Mt. Eden. We will definitely be ordering from here whenever we want pizza in this area. 5/5
